parameters: \C[23]I can't leave right now. I was told to wait here...
Just sh-it tight. Sh-omeone will come shortly.
\C[23]Mwahaha! You were hoping this place would be gender neutral, weren't you?
\C[23]N-No....! Well, okay... Maybe a little bit...
\C[23]I can hear people whispering through the crack...
You love that boy a lot.
W-What other way could there be?
Don't put an act on me.
I've known you for a while now.
You even came to church to confess.
I... I don't know what you're talking about.
I heard him say that you two are on a date.
You're in love with him, aren't you?
I... I do feel jittery when I'm around him.
Have you been intimate with him?
No! Not really... I mean... Of course not...!
Well... What are you waiting for?
P-Please don't say things like that when he's around!
Heh... You're such an open book.
Oh, sorry! I wasn't listening or anything...
Your sponge is inside the drawer over there.
The bucket is under the table.
I'll leave you to it then...
Aren't I supposed to get a massage?
I'm sure you can handle it yourself.
It's not that I want a massage from you, but... I did pay for it.
Do you even know what our services are, boy?
What?! No\..\..\.. Ugh! Yuck! Ewww\..\..\.. Blech!
I mean... Not that there's anything wrong with that...
Yeah, well... Consider yourself lucky then!
I don't have time for this.
\C[23]I just hope Mom is having a better time.
\C[23]Wait a minute\..\..\.. If they're giving a sex massage...
